msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:72
msgid ""
"When called with only scalars, ``np.block`` is equivalent to an ndarray "
"call. So ``np.block([[1, 2], [3, 4]])`` is equivalent to ``np.array([[1, 2], "
"[3, 4]])``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:76
msgid ""
"This function does not enforce that the blocks lie on a fixed grid. ``np."
"block([[a, b], [c, d]])`` is not restricted to arrays of the form::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:79
msgid ""
"AAAbb\n"
"AAAbb\n"
"cccDD"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:83
msgid "But is also allowed to produce, for some ``a, b, c, d``::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:85
msgid ""
"AAAbb\n"
"AAAbb\n"
"cDDDD"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:89
msgid ""
"Since concatenation happens along the last axis first, `block` is *not* "
"capable of producing the following directly::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:92
msgid ""
"AAAbb\n"
"cccbb\n"
"cccDD"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.block:96
msgid ""
"Matlab's \"square bracket stacking\", ``[A, B, ...; p, q, ...]``, is "
"equivalent to ``np.block([[A, B, ...], [p, q, ...]])``."
msgstr ""

